    {
      "actionDate": "2025-02-04",
      "actionDesc": "Reported to House",
      "text": "<p>This resolution provides for consideration of H.R. 27, the<em> Halt All Lethal Trafficking of&nbsp;Fentanyl Act </em>or the <em>HALT Fentanyl Act.</em> Specifically, it waives all points of order against consideration of the bill.</p><p>Under the resolution, the bill is to be considered as amended according to changes by the Rules Committee in its report accompanying the&nbsp;resolution.</p>",
      "updateDate": "2026-06-29T19:27:29Z",
